Version 0.3.0
-------------
- Fixed a bug that made the X server crash when loading the thumbnails.
  Obviously, the images were released too often.
- Added support for user directories as specified by freedesktop.org
  by linking with FreeDesktopKit framework (on demand, only).
- Add support for creating timestamp directories below the directory
  selected for image import.
- Set the import directory once via the preferences and not each time
  the user imports images.
- Do not overwrite images with the same name when importing. Instead
  append a number to make the name unique.

Version 0.2.1
-------------
- The inspector window no longer jumps to its last saved position,
  but immediately opens there.

Version 0.2.0
-------------
- Read extended image data (EXIF) and display it in the inspector.
- Show thumbnails in correct orientation (landscape, portrait).
- Fixed a memory leak.

Version 0.1.1
-------------
- Fixed a crash when downloading/deleting images.
- Clean up GNUmakefile.preamble.
- Beautify drop shadows.

Version 0.1.0
-------------
First release.
